It seems like a great app but needs a little more polish to be sensational.

should return to the previous view. Etc etc.

Just a note to everyone. This is a beautiful app to be sure, but be prepared to spend $8 if you want the solar system AND the ability to look at the 3d spacecraft. Yes it says in app purchases,  but you would think that in the app called Solar Walk 2, 3d spacecraft and missions, when you pay your $3 you would get 3d spacecraft & missions. You dont. To get those spacecraft and missions you need to pay (for the second time) a fee ranging from $1-$5 depending on if you want the spacecraft & missions available for timeperiods from one month ($1) to permanently ($5). Im cool with In app purchases,  but dont call your app "3d spacecraft & space missions", and then charge extra for 3d spacecraft & missions. This developer is in Germany so hopefully something was lost in translation when they wrote the description, ill chalk it up to that, otherwise their just shady. It probably doesnt count for anything but this is one disappointed customer. In the words of our dear leader.........SAD.
